Westside Outbound

Description:

The Westside Outbound leaves campus and travels through Floral Avenue in Johnson City and Main Street in Binghamton enroute to the University Downtown Center.

Operation Time:

Weekdays:
7:15 A.M. to 11:45 P.M. (Monday-Thursdays) or 11:00 P.M. (Fridays)


Weekends:
9:15 A.M. to 11:00 P.M. (Saturdays) or 12:00 A.M. (Sundays)

Notes:

Scroll below for a graphic map of the Westside Outbound, its schedule, and the stops along its route.


For Friday and Saturday nights after 12:00 A.M. please refer to the Late Night WS Outbound, unless otherwise posted.
